snippet.textDisplay:
As an Indian, I may feel a hint of envy toward Pakistan's rich musical heritage, but my appreciation transcends borders. Pakistani music's depth and soulfulness, from classical qawwalis to vibrant folk tunes, are a testament to a culture steeped in musical brilliance. While I celebrate India's musical diversity, I can't help but admire and learn from Pakistan's melodic treasures...
Loads of love from india..
